{"word":"ἀνατολή","slug":"ἀνατολή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνατολή</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀνατέλλω'><el>ἀνατέλλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a rising, rise</i>, of the sun, often in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; of the stars, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>the quarter of sunrise, East</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>Oriens</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}